				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>N. Y.</placeName> <date>July 21&#44; 1854</date>&#45;</p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44;</p>
				<p>Peace&#44; as usual&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Please send me the year&#39;s &#8220;Occident&#8221; from <date>April 1853</date> to<lb/> <date>April 1854</date>&#44; along with your deliver of next <date>August</date>&#44; through <persName>Mr. Cantor</persName>&#44;<lb/> <placeName>56 Duane Street</placeName>.  If I should not sell it&#44; I will return it to you<lb/> cost free.  AS to news&#44; the rumour is current here that <persName>Dr. Illoway</persName><lb/> will deliver his trial sermon at the Broadway synagogue in <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>&#44;<lb/> on <date>Sabbath Nahamu</date>.&#42;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">With every respect and friendship&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Michael Light</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>42 Oliver Street</placeName></p>
				<p>&#42;The <date>Sabbath Nahamu</date> is the one immediately after <date>Tish&#39;a b&#45;av</date></p>
